All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
public class ChannelException
extends VException

This runtime exception is thrown when a channel command such as newChannel, delete, enable or disable could not be completed because the event daemon did not complete the channel command and returned a failure status.
